];
const faqItems = [
  { q: "Does ServiceTitan publish pricing on their website?", a: "No. ServiceTitan requires you to sit through a sales demo before receiving a quote. Pricing is negotiated individually based on company size, number of technicians, and contract length. The ranges in this article are compiled from verified user reports, review platforms, and BBB filings." },
  { q: "What is the minimum team size for ServiceTitan?", a: "ServiceTitan is designed for companies with 3 or more technicians. They have stated publicly that their platform is not optimized for companies with 3 or fewer technicians. Most users report the platform delivers ROI for teams of 10+ techs." },
  { q: "Can I get out of a ServiceTitan contract early?", a: "ServiceTitan uses annual contracts (often multi-year for better rates). Early termination fees apply. Multiple BBB complaints describe difficulty canceling even at contract end. Check your renewal date and cancellation terms carefully." },
