  { q: "What are the cheapest ServiceTitan alternatives?", a: "Jobber starts at $39/month for solo operators. Housecall Pro starts at $59/month. Workiz starts at $49/month. All three offer free trials. See our full guide to ServiceTitan alternatives for scored comparisons." }
];
